'''夏利萊大宅'''（{{lang-en|Harilela Mansion}}），位於[[香港|香港]][[九龍|九龍]][[窩打老道|窩打老道]]與[[對衡道|對衡道]]交界的綠色大屋<ref name="大公報">{{cite news |title=夏利莱家族70人同住印式大宅 |url=http://news.takungpao.com/hkol/topnews/2014-12/2874468.html |language=zh |publisher=[[大公報|大公報]] |date=2014-12-31 |accessdate=2015-08-15 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304090955/http://news.takungpao.com/hkol/topnews/2014-12/2874468.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是源自[[英屬印度|英屬印度]][[信德族|信德族]]的香港望族[[夏利里拉家族|夏利萊氏]]（{{lang|en|Harilela}}）的住宅，現居住了家族三代逾100名成員<ref name="DNA">{{cite news |title=110-member NRI family resides under one roof |url=http://www.dnaindia.com/world/report-110-member-nri-family-resides-under-one-roof-4240 |language=en |publisher=DNA India |date=2005-10-02 |accessdate=2015-08-16 |archive-date=2015-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925062914/http://www.dnaindia.com/world/report-110-member-nri-family-resides-under-one-roof-4240 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="SCMP">{{cite news |title=How do 90 Harilelas get along under one roof? With plenty of respect |url=http://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/article/1204956/how-do-90-harilelas-get-along-under-one-roof-plenty-respect |language=en |author=Dennis Chong |publisher=[[South_China_Morning_Post|South China Morning Post]] |date=2013-04-02 |accessdate=2015-08-16 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924181504/http://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/article/1204956/how-do-90-harilelas-get-along-under-one-roof-plenty-respect |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 簡介 ==
大宅全屋以高牆圍著，分為新舊兩翼，以印度姬陵式設計<ref name="大公報" />。舊翼用了3年時間籌備，1年時間興建，於1952年落成，原本只有18個房間，是夏利萊母親的遺願，希望他與6名兄弟永遠住在一起<ref name="DNA" />，亦兌現夏利萊事業成功前已經許下「能共患難富貴」的承諾<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Hari：Aron Harilela 引領奢華酒店新浪潮|url=https://www.tatlerasia.com/power-purpose/business/aron-harilela-luxury-hotel-project-the-hari-hong-kong-zh-hant|access-date=2022-02-19|author=Eric Wilson|date=2021-08-05|publisher=Tatler Asia|archive-date=2022-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220219150040/https://www.tatlerasia.com/power-purpose/business/aron-harilela-luxury-hotel-project-the-hari-hong-kong-zh-hant|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來，因為家庭成員不斷增加，需要重新裝修，並且興建了新翼的部分<ref name="Hindu">{{cite news |title=Meet Hong Kong's Harilelas |url=http://www.hinduismtoday.com/modules/smartsection/item.php?itemid=3186 |language=en |publisher=Hinduism Today |accessdate=2015-08-15 |archive-date=2015-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905180703/http://www.hinduismtoday.com/modules/smartsection/item.php?itemid=3186 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。現在，大屋樓高3層，另設一層地庫，總面積達{{convert|50000|sqft}}，共有90個房間(40間睡房)(40間浴室)、多個裝飾宏偉的客廳、一個設有75座位的電影院，另有祈禱室<ref>{{cite web|url=https://s3.us-west-1.wasabisys.com/pl-library/books/ac0612f5b7a46bef35d035b7bb1f3d0b.pdf|title=香港百人∙下冊 (頁320-325)|publisher=亞洲電視|access-date=2020-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200423195339/https://s3.us-west-1.wasabisys.com/pl-library/books/ac0612f5b7a46bef35d035b7bb1f3d0b.pdf|archive-date=2020-04-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、保齡球場、健身房、桑拿房、游泳池、按摩浴池、酒吧區等，儼然是個自成格局的小社區。地庫則可以停泊70輛汽車<ref>{{cite news |title=Richest Indian in Hong Kong |url=http://www.tribuneindia.com/2007/20070708/spectrum/society1.htm |language=en |author=Ramkiran Mehta |publisher=The Tribune |date=2007-07-08 |accessdate=2015-08-15 |archive-date=2015-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150708162234/http://www.tribuneindia.com/2007/20070708/spectrum/society1.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=走进富豪家——到夏利莱家作客 |url=http://lizust.blog.163.com/blog/static/88513111201057103338970/ |language=zh |author=夏木 |date=2010-06-07 |accessdate=2015-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304224636/http://lizust.blog.163.com/blog/static/88513111201057103338970/ |archive-date=2016-03-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

每逢星期日，家族成員都會聚餐<ref>{{cite news |title=家族70口同住五萬呎大宅 |url=http://news.singtao.ca/toronto/2014-12-30/hongkong1419924180d5381821.html |language=zh |publisher=[[星島日報|星島日報]] |date=2014-12-30 |accessdate=2015-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180214091734/http://news.singtao.ca/toronto/2014-12-30/hongkong1419924180d5381821.html |archive-date=2018-02-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，差不多隔日都有大大小小的生日會或其他類型的慶祝活動。他們聘請了30個僕人、3個廚師、幾個修理技工、1個園丁、7個司機和1個裁縫，以維持每日的起居作息<ref name="Hindu" />。

